{"tid":907854,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"大聲屌柒起地鐵傾電話 唔插耳機打機既人","createTime":"2018-11-19T06:48:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-19T07:01:26.000Z","uid":140633,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d07a1b4ed698f4df38ca5d2ab19be98537e18e18","tid":907854,"uid":140633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T06:48:08.000Z","msg":"如果你唔屌柒佢地 到時香港就通街都係啲咁既人<br />\n尤其係啲大媽廢老蝗蟲bb<br />\n<br />\n當然啦 作為一個有文化既人<br />\n唔會一黎屌柒人架嘛<br />\n好聲好氣勸兩句先<br />\n唔得先開火架嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果你唔帶頭 或者唔幫手 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">你就係助長緊呢啲事情發生</span><br />\n望咩望<br />\n係你啊仆街<br />\n<br />\n屌完大媽有感"},{"pid":"ab8bc2d42bf2bbfc7d5660b228824276855ce066","tid":907854,"uid":119959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T06:50:02.000Z","msg":"details pls"},{"pid":"1161bbea39f7653c15844cf21043f1d04a291841","tid":907854,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T06:53:21.000Z","msg":"如果係老野<br />\n<br />\n我會起佢隔離鬥大聲播Mastamic 首破地獄"},{"pid":"147b22a6b197a02317b5149b9f9cec4a3052fd9d","tid":907854,"uid":140633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1161bbea39f7653c15844cf21043f1d04a291841","tid":907854,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T06:53:21.000Z","msg":"如果係老野<br />\n<br />\n我會起佢隔離鬥大聲播Mastamic 首破地獄"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T06:55:36.000Z","msg":"咁咪嘈親其他人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29335432825f1ec4c5ad270ac6a168eafb33e721","tid":907854,"uid":140633,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ab8bc2d42bf2bbfc7d5660b228824276855ce066","tid":907854,"uid":119959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T06:50:02.000Z","msg":"details pls"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T07:01:26.000Z","msg":"個大媽好大聲傾電話 <br />\n我細聲勸完佢 佢肯收線既<br />\n<br />\n好死唔死佢加多句<br />\n「咁唔鐘意咪行去前面坐囉」<br />\n<br />\n即刻屎都滾撚埋 <br />\n好彩下站落車<br />\n<br />\n補多句<br />\n「你後面個女人嫌你嘈得濟 行走左啦」<br />\n「成架車得你一條友嘈煩」<br />\n「做翻個有文化有禮貌既人啦」"}]}